{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/blueutil/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Funny Eagle","author":"Jason Yang"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"ec36d7d5-7324-5b44-88c9-e4ff79c2c67c","excerpt":"我希望开机后自动连接小米蓝牙音箱，在MAC OSX的设置界面，没有找到相关的设置。于是在网上找到了blueutil，分分钟轻松搞定。 安装 使用安装  查看使用说明 查看配对设备  通过ID连接设备…","html":"<p>我希望开机后自动连接小米蓝牙音箱，在MAC OSX的设置界面，没有找到相关的设置。于是在网上找到了<a href=\"https://github.com/toy/blueutil\">blueutil</a>，分分钟轻松搞定。</p>\n<h3 id=\"安装code-classlanguage-textblueutilcode\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85code-classlanguage-textblueutilcode\" aria-label=\"安装code classlanguage textblueutilcode permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>安装<code class=\"language-text\">blueutil</code></h3>\n<p>使用<code class=\"language-text\">homebrew</code>安装<code class=\"language-text\">blueutil</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">brew <span class=\"token function\">install</span> blueutil</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"code-classlanguage-textblueutil--hcode-查看使用说明\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#code-classlanguage-textblueutil--hcode-%E6%9F%A5%E7%9C%8B%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E\" aria-label=\"code classlanguage textblueutil  hcode 查看使用说明 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><code class=\"language-text\">blueutil -h</code> 查看使用说明</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">yangjl@Mac ~ % blueutil <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-h</span>\nblueutil v2.9.1\n\nUsage:\n  blueutil <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>options<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">..</span>.</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"查看配对设备-code-classlanguage-textblueutil---pairedcode\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%9F%A5%E7%9C%8B%E9%85%8D%E5%AF%B9%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87-code-classlanguage-textblueutil---pairedcode\" aria-label=\"查看配对设备 code classlanguage textblueutil   pairedcode permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>查看配对设备 <code class=\"language-text\">blueutil --paired</code></h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">yangjl@Mac ~ % blueutil <span class=\"token parameter variable\">--paired</span> \naddress: <span class=\"token number\">64</span>-64-4a-7f-ad-85, connected <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>master, <span class=\"token number\">0</span> dBm<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>, not favourite, paired, name: <span class=\"token string\">\"小米音箱-蓝牙\"</span>, recent access date: <span class=\"token number\">2023</span>-11-27 <span class=\"token number\">10</span>:57:15 +0000\naddress: <span class=\"token number\">74</span>-45-ce-dd-37-e6, not connected, not favourite, paired, name: <span class=\"token string\">\"ATH-M20xBT \"</span>, recent access date: <span class=\"token number\">2023</span>-11-27 <span class=\"token number\">10</span>:57:15 +0000</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"通过id连接设备-code-classlanguage-textblueutil---connect-idcode\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87id%E8%BF%9E%E6%8E%A5%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87-code-classlanguage-textblueutil---connect-idcode\" aria-label=\"通过id连接设备 code classlanguage textblueutil   connect idcode permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>通过ID连接设备 <code class=\"language-text\">blueutil --connect ID</code></h3>\n<p>上一步<code class=\"language-text\">address</code>的值就是ID，在终端输入 <code class=\"language-text\">blueutil --connect 设备ID</code>即可</p>\n<h3 id=\"查看已连接蓝牙设备-code-classlanguage-textblueutil---connected-code\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%9F%A5%E7%9C%8B%E5%B7%B2%E8%BF%9E%E6%8E%A5%E8%93%9D%E7%89%99%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87-code-classlanguage-textblueutil---connected-code\" aria-label=\"查看已连接蓝牙设备 code classlanguage textblueutil   connected code permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>查看已连接蓝牙设备 <code class=\"language-text\">blueutil --connected </code></h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">yangjl@Mac ~ % blueutil <span class=\"token parameter variable\">--connected</span>                \naddress: <span class=\"token number\">64</span>-64-4a-7f-ad-85, connected <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>master, <span class=\"token number\">0</span> dBm<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>, not favourite, paired, name: <span class=\"token string\">\"小米音箱-蓝牙\"</span>, recent access date: <span class=\"token number\">2023</span>-11-27 <span class=\"token number\">10</span>:59:40 +0000</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"设置自动连接\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E8%87%AA%E5%8A%A8%E8%BF%9E%E6%8E%A5\" aria-label=\"设置自动连接 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>设置自动连接</h3>\n<p>创建一个文件<code class=\"language-text\">auto_connect_bluetooth.sh</code>，文件内容如下，其中ID自行修改，</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">blueutil <span class=\"token parameter variable\">--connect</span> <span class=\"token number\">64</span>-64-4a-7f-ad-85\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">echo</span> <span class=\"token string\">'自动连接蓝牙至小米音箱'</span>\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">exit</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>在终端执行<code class=\"language-text\">chmod +x auto_connect_bluetooth.sh</code>为文件增加执行权限。</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">系统偏好设置</code> -> <code class=\"language-text\">用户与群组</code> -> <code class=\"language-text\">登陆项</code> -> <code class=\"language-text\">+</code> -> 选择 `auto_connect_bluetooth.sh“</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/3ea6014aa4000247c27d86817d5f492b/74866/image.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Alt text\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/3ea6014aa4000247c27d86817d5f492b/fcda8/image.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/3ea6014aa4000247c27d86817d5f492b/12f09/image.png 148w,\n/static/3ea6014aa4000247c27d86817d5f492b/e4a3f/image.png 295w,\n/static/3ea6014aa4000247c27d86817d5f492b/fcda8/image.png 590w,\n/static/3ea6014aa4000247c27d86817d5f492b/74866/image.png 668w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>另外建议把shell窗口设置的退出策略修改一下，这样执行完终端窗口就自动关